          "title": "The verb you give the user",
          "body": "Tinder did more than ship a faster tap. It gave dating a public verb. \"Swipe right\" left the app and entered ordinary speech, which is how a one-screen gesture became a category-defining product. [venturebeat-badeen-2016]",
