          "title": "No website, no app, just a chat server",
          "body": "In March 2022, David Holz launched Midjourney's closed beta inside a Discord server. Users typed prompts as chat messages, watched images generate in public channels, and invited friends before a single line of marketing copy was written. [midjourney-verge]",
