          "id": "lesson",
          "title": "Distribution is a design decision",
          "body": "Holz did not treat distribution as a separate problem to solve after the product was ready. He made a specific platform choice , Discord , that embedded distribution into the act of using the product. Creation was public. Public creation was advertising.",
